'''印度－尼日利亞關係'''，是指[[印度共和國|印度共和國]]和[[奈及利亞聯邦共和國|奈及利亞聯邦共和國]]之間的雙邊關係。近年兩國之間的經貿關係日漸緊密：例如尼日利亞的[[石油|石油]]資源豐富，印度近年已經取代美國，成為尼日利亞最大的[[原油|原油]]出口國<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/business/india-business/Nigeria-says-India-now-its-largest-crude-importer/articleshow/36831221.cms |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2014-07-10 |archive-date=2014-07-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140719192810/http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/business/india-business/Nigeria-says-India-now-its-largest-crude-importer/articleshow/36831221.cms |dead-url=no }}</ref>，又計劃在尼日利亞設立[[煉油廠|煉油廠]]<ref>[http://www.bloomberg.com/apps/news?pid=20601091&sid=at4XhhZvOCt8 ONGC Mittal Drills Nigerian Offshore Oil Block 279 ]</ref>。

== 背景 ==
印度和尼日利亞同樣曾是[[大英帝國|大英帝國]]的殖民地。印度一向支持尼日利亞擺脫殖民統治；於尼日利亞正式獨立的兩年前（1958年），已在該國設有[[外交代表機構|外交代表機構]]<ref name="C">{{cite web |title=PM to visit Nigeria to enhance bilateral ties |url=http://www.rediff.com/news/2007/oct/09pm.htm |publisher=[[Rediff.com|Rediff.com]] |date=2007-10-09 |accessdate=2008-06-21 |archive-date=2019-10-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191023062618/https://www.rediff.com/news/2007/oct/09pm.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="MO">{{cite web |title=Nigeria: "India's Exports Hit $875m" |url=http://allafrica.com/stories/200710140023.html |publisher=This Day (Lagos), allAfrica.com |date=2007-10-14 |accessdate=2008-06-21 |archive-date=2012-10-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121004051259/http://allafrica.com/stories/200710140023.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Q">{{cite web |title=India will continue on high growth rate path: PM |url=http://www.expressindia.com/latest-news/India-will-continue-on-high-growth-rate-path-PM/228551/ |publisher=[[Indian_Express|Indian Express]], Express India |date=2007-10-15 |accessdate=2008-06-21 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081010001734/http://www.expressindia.com/latest-news/India-will-continue-on-high-growth-rate-path-PM/228551/ |archivedate=2008-10-10 }}</ref><ref name="Z">{{cite web |title=Indo-Nigerian relations |url=http://www.meaindia.nic.in/foreignrelation/11fr12.pdf |format=PDF |publisher=[[Ministry_of_External_Affairs_(India)|Ministry of External Affairs (India)]] |accessdate=2008-06-21 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080911035423/http://www.meaindia.nic.in/foreignrelation/11fr12.pdf |archivedate=2008-09-11 }}</ref>。兩國同樣擁有多樣的自然和經濟資源，是各自的區域最大的經濟體。兩者均是[[英聯邦國家|英聯邦國家]]、[[七十七国集团|七十七国集团]]和[[不結盟運動|不結盟運動]]的成員<ref name="B">{{cite web |title=Indian Prime Minister to visit Nigeria |url=http://www.mynaijanews.com/content/view/754/2/ |publisher=My Naija News |date=2007-10-11 |accessdate=2008-06-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170405171009/http://www.mynaijanews.com/content/view/754/2/ |archive-date=2017-04-05 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

== 商貿關係 ==
尼日利亞在1998-99年恢復民主後，兩國之間的經貿關係日漸緊密，雙邊貿易總額由當時的約3億[[美元|美元]]攀升至2005-06年的約9億美元<ref name="MO" />。截至2007年，兩國之間的非石油雙邊貿易總額估計為六十至八十億美元<ref name="C" /><ref name="MO" />。於2006年四月至九月期間，尼日利亞到印度的出口總額為四十億美元，印度到尼日利亞的出口總額則為8.75億美元<ref name="MO" />。印度企業在尼日利亞的[[製造業|製造業]]、[[醫藥|醫藥]]、[[塑料業|塑料業]]、[[鋼鐵工業|鋼鐵工業]]、[[工程|工程]]、[[信息技術|信息技術]]和[[通訊|通訊]]等範疇巨額地投資<ref name="MO" />；尼日利亞亦鼓勵印度企業積極地在尼日利亞投資及開採[[煤礦|煤礦]]、[[金礦|金礦]]、[[鐵礦|鐵礦]]等礦產資源<ref name="MA">{{cite web |title=Nigeria ready to partner India in mining |url=http://www.thehindubusinessline.com/2007/10/17/stories/2007101750901200.htm |publisher=[[The_Hindu|The Hindu Business Line]] |date=2007-10-17 |accessdate=2008-06-21 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100203064135/http://www.thehindubusinessline.com/2007/10/17/stories/2007101750901200.htm |archivedate=2010-02-03 }}</ref>。

尼日利亞是印度在非洲最大的原油進口國，平均每天有40萬桶由尼日利亞出口至印度，總值100億美元<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.vanguardngr.com/2010/02/01/india-seeks-expansion-of-oil-trade-with-nigeria/ |title=India seeks expansion of oil trade with Nigeria |access-date=2014-07-10 |archive-date=2010-03-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100312035623/http://www.vanguardngr.com/2010/02/01/india-seeks-expansion-of-oil-trade-with-nigeria/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

